      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable sedan in good condition, well-suited for a driver seeking a reliable and well-maintained vehicle. The exterior remains in great shape, showing only minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a smooth engine and transmission that have been regularly serviced. This is a great opportunity to own a quality car that balances performance and value perfectly.",
