      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering a linear power band through individual throttle bodies. All critical preventive maintenance is documented: rod bearings have been replaced, the double VANOS system overhauled, and the rear subframe reinforced with a bespoke plate kit. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity,",
