      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. This car has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, which is immediately evident in the deep, mirror-like luster of the original factory paint\u2014entirely free from swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, retaining that distinct 'new car' aroma with absolutely no signs of bolster wear, creasing, or fading. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been serviced strictly by certified master technicians ahead of every recommended interval, and I have a comprehensive binder of all service records available for review. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of road salt or inclement weather use. From the crystal-clear infotainment display to the tactile response of every button and switch, every feature functions exactly as it did the",
